1
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:08,241
JoJo: DOWN HERE,

2
00:00:08,308 --> 00:00:10,443
MY HAMON WILL HIT YOU
ALL THE HARDER.

3
00:00:11,444 --> 00:00:19,019
UNDERWATER
TURQUOISE BLUE OVERDRIVE!

4
00:00:19,119 --> 00:00:21,922
( Blueford yells )

5
00:00:23,023 --> 00:00:23,924
Speedwagon: HE DID IT!

6
00:00:23,990 --> 00:00:25,158
‐ Zeppeli: BRAVO.
‐ ( Tarukus grunts )

7
00:00:25,191 --> 00:00:26,527
Poco: THAT WAS AMAZING.

8
00:00:26,627 --> 00:00:27,994
JoJo: IT'S NOT OVER YET!

9
00:00:28,028 --> 00:00:30,697
I CAN'T BELIEVE BLUEFORD
WAS ABLE TO DODGE

10
00:00:30,764 --> 00:00:33,867
THAT BLAST OF HAMON.
HE MOVES SO FAST UNDERWATER.

11
00:00:33,934 --> 00:00:35,702
HE WAS ALL A BLUR.

12
00:00:35,802 --> 00:00:39,506
MY OVERDRIVE
BARELY GLANCED OFF HIS FOREHEAD.

13
00:00:39,540 --> 00:00:41,975
NOW I KNOW ANYTHING LESS
THAN A SOLID PUNCH

14
00:00:42,042 --> 00:00:44,645
WON'T BE ENOUGH
TO SEND THE HAMON INTO HIM.

15
00:00:44,711 --> 00:00:48,649
Blueford: MY GOOD LORD DIO,
I THANK THEE FOR THIS LIFE ANEW

16
00:00:48,715 --> 00:00:51,017
THAT I MAY DUEL
WITH THIS STOUTHEARTED LAD.

17
00:00:51,051 --> 00:00:54,020
MY HEART WOULD SWELL TO BURSTING
IF STILL IT BEAT.

18
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:57,891
IN BLOOD AND DEED,
HE IS THE STUFF OF HEROES.

19
00:00:57,958 --> 00:01:01,067
NOW WE WILL FIGHT
IN OUR NATIVE ELEMENT.

20
00:01:01,134 --> 00:01:03,136
IT IS BY MASTERY OF OUR ARTS

21
00:01:03,203 --> 00:01:06,472
AND STRENGTH OF OUR SPIRITS
THAT WE WAGE THIS DUEL.

22
00:01:06,540 --> 00:01:08,708
BARE YOUR SOUL.
HOLD NOTHING BACK,

23
00:01:08,742 --> 00:01:11,311
LEST YOU NOT SURVIVE
BEYOND THIS MOMENT!

24
00:01:11,377 --> 00:01:14,314
( yells )

25
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:15,582
JoJo: EVEN AS DIO'S PUPPET,

26
00:01:15,649 --> 00:01:18,151
HIS PRIDE IS A FORCE
TO BE RECKONED WITH,

27
00:01:18,218 --> 00:01:19,485
BUT HIS KNIGHTLY VALOR

28
00:01:19,553 --> 00:01:22,022
HAS BEEN TWISTED
INTO A WANTON LOVE OF VIOLENCE.

29
00:01:22,088 --> 00:01:23,256
Blueford: WHEN I BEST YOU,

30
00:01:23,356 --> 00:01:24,891
I'LL TAKE YOUR HEAD
AS MY TROPHY!

31
00:01:24,925 --> 00:01:27,493
JoJo: IT'S EASY TO LET
YOUR HAIR DO THE WORK.

32
00:01:27,561 --> 00:01:30,096
COME. WITHSTAND MY HAMON
FACE TO FACE LIKE A MAN!

33
00:01:33,166 --> 00:01:35,101
♪

34
00:01:42,408 --> 00:01:44,745
( singing in Japanese )

35
00:03:05,839 --> 00:03:07,674
♪

36
00:03:07,708 --> 00:03:11,545
JoJo: OVERDRIVE BARRAGE!

37
00:03:13,046 --> 00:03:14,981
( grunting )

38
00:03:17,483 --> 00:03:19,686
( screams )

39
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,887
Zeppeli: JOJO!

40
00:03:28,394 --> 00:03:29,830
THIS IS TERRIBLE.

41
00:03:29,896 --> 00:03:32,866
HAMON CAN ONLY BE PROJECTED
THROUGH THE ARMS AND THE LEGS.

42
00:03:32,899 --> 00:03:35,636
WITH HIS ARMS BOUND
IN FRONT OF HIM LIKE THAT,

43
00:03:35,702 --> 00:03:37,137
HE HAS NO WAY OF BLASTING

44
00:03:37,203 --> 00:03:38,839
THROUGH THAT INFERNAL HAIR
OF BLUEFORD'S.

45
00:03:38,905 --> 00:03:40,507
Speedwagon:
I‐I WANNA HELP HIM OUT,

46
00:03:40,574 --> 00:03:42,809
BUT YOU AND ME
HAVE GOT THINGS EVEN WORSE.

47
00:03:42,876 --> 00:03:47,013
I THINK OL' TARUKUS
FANCIES A DUST‐UP.

48
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:49,650
( JoJo screaming )

49
00:03:49,716 --> 00:03:52,586
HIS HAIR,
IT'S TEARING THROUGH MY CLOTHES.

50
00:03:52,686 --> 00:03:54,054
THROUGH MY SKIN.

51
00:03:54,087 --> 00:03:56,757
THE MORE I STRUGGLE,
THE TIGHTER IT WINDS,

52
00:03:56,857 --> 00:03:59,259
AND IT'S SUCKING MY BLOOD AWAY.

53
00:03:59,359 --> 00:04:01,267
( grunting )

54
00:04:03,937 --> 00:04:05,939
Blueford:
BID YOUR PETTY LIFE ADIEU.

55
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:07,874
BEHOLD, THE COUP DE GR ÂCE!

56
00:04:07,941 --> 00:04:09,109
I'LL TAKE YOUR HEAD

57
00:04:09,175 --> 00:04:13,046
AND BATHE IN A FOUNTAIN
OF LIFE‐GIVING BLOOD!

58
00:04:13,113 --> 00:04:14,347
JoJo: TAKE THIS!

59
00:04:14,414 --> 00:04:16,883
( inhales )

60
00:04:16,950 --> 00:04:19,285
♪

61
00:04:21,021 --> 00:04:23,189
WATER'S NOT ALL
THAT CONDUCTS HAMON.

62
00:04:23,256 --> 00:04:26,126
METAL SILVER OVERDRIVE!

63
00:04:27,694 --> 00:04:29,095
‐ ( Tarukus grunts )
‐ Speedwagon: WHAT A BRAIN.

64
00:04:29,129 --> 00:04:30,797
USING THE SWORD
TO HOIST BLUEFORD

65
00:04:30,864 --> 00:04:33,366
BY HIS OWN BLEEDING PETARD.
WHO THINKS OF THAT?

66
00:04:36,636 --> 00:04:38,972
JoJo: HOW MY HEART RESONATES.

67
00:04:39,038 --> 00:04:41,441
I'M PULSING WITH HEAT AND LIFE.

68
00:04:41,474 --> 00:04:43,744
( breathes deeply )

69
00:04:43,810 --> 00:04:46,547
MY VERY BLOOD
IS A SYMPHONY WITHIN ME!

70
00:04:46,613 --> 00:04:51,618
SUNLIGHT YELLOW OVERDRIVE!

71
00:04:51,652 --> 00:04:52,986
( Blueford groans )

72
00:04:53,086 --> 00:04:54,655
‐ ( Zeppeli gasps )
‐ Speedwagon: THERE WE GO.

73
00:04:54,721 --> 00:04:58,224
THAT'S IT. ABOUT TIME WE HEARD
THE WELCOME CRACKLE OF HAMON.

74
00:04:58,291 --> 00:05:00,627
( JoJo exhales )

75
00:05:00,661 --> 00:05:02,969
WHEN I PUMMELED BLUEFORD
A MOMENT AGO,

76
00:05:03,003 --> 00:05:05,338
SOMETHING FELT DIFFERENT.
KNOWING HIS PAST

77
00:05:05,405 --> 00:05:07,808
MAKES HIS PRESENT CORRUPTION
ALL THE WORSE.

78
00:05:07,841 --> 00:05:11,144
TAKE HEART, JOJO.
HE IS THAT MAN NO LONGER.

79
00:05:11,177 --> 00:05:15,115
HE'S NOTHING BUT A ZOMBIE
EAGER TO SPREAD HIS EVIL.

80
00:05:15,181 --> 00:05:18,018
YOU MUST BE THE ONE TO END HIM.

81
00:05:18,118 --> 00:05:20,854
( sizzling )

82
00:05:20,921 --> 00:05:24,257
Blueford: I AM
THE BLACK KNIGHT BLUEFORD.

83
00:05:24,324 --> 00:05:26,459
STRIKE ME AS THOU WILT.

84
00:05:26,527 --> 00:05:27,460
THIS PAIN IS NOTHING!

85
00:05:28,795 --> 00:05:30,531
Speedwagon:
HE'S STILL DANGEROUS, MATE!

86
00:05:30,597 --> 00:05:31,765
LOOK OUT!

87
00:05:32,933 --> 00:05:35,802
EVEN MISSING AN ARM
AND SCORCHED ALL TO HELL,

88
00:05:35,869 --> 00:05:39,105
HE'S LAYING INTO JOJO
EVERY BIT AS FEROCIOUSLY.

89
00:05:41,207 --> 00:05:42,308
( both gasp )

90
00:05:42,375 --> 00:05:43,644
Speedwagon: WHAT THE?!

91
00:05:43,710 --> 00:05:45,445
DON'T JUST STAND THERE!
DO SOMETHING!

92
00:05:45,512 --> 00:05:49,049
IF YOU DON'T GET OUTTA THERE
NOW, IT'S CURTAINS FOR YOU!

93
00:05:54,555 --> 00:05:56,990
HAVE THEY BOTH GONE MAD?

94
00:05:57,057 --> 00:05:59,359
WHAT ARE THEY DOIN', EH?

95
00:05:59,392 --> 00:06:00,567
( sizzling )

96
00:06:00,667 --> 00:06:02,569
JoJo: A MOMENT AGO,

97
00:06:02,636 --> 00:06:04,738
YOU SAID,
"THIS PAIN IS NOTHING."

98
00:06:04,838 --> 00:06:09,409
THAT MEANS PAIN IS SOMETHING
YOU CAN FEEL AGAIN.

99
00:06:09,475 --> 00:06:10,877
♪

100
00:06:10,911 --> 00:06:13,013
( Zeppeli gasps )
THE FLOWERS,

101
00:06:13,079 --> 00:06:15,081
THEY'RE BLOOMING
ALL AROUND HIM.

102
00:06:15,181 --> 00:06:17,918
EVEN NOW, THE HAMON
RAVAGES THE EVIL

103
00:06:18,018 --> 00:06:21,187
THAT ANIMATES
BLUEFORD'S LONG‐DEAD CORPSE.

104
00:06:24,725 --> 00:06:28,094
YOU SEE? THE LONG‐FORGOTTEN PAIN
CAME BACK.

105
00:06:28,161 --> 00:06:30,664
ONLY HUMANS KNOW
THAT SORT OF ACHE.

106
00:06:30,731 --> 00:06:33,233
OBSERVE, MY DEAR SPEEDWAGON.

107
00:06:33,266 --> 00:06:35,769
HIS ZOMBIE BODY
SUCCUMBS TO THE HAMON,

108
00:06:35,836 --> 00:06:38,872
BUT HIS NOBLE SOUL
IS REDEEMED IN THE PROCESS.

109
00:06:38,939 --> 00:06:41,074
JoJo: I COULD SENSE
THE GOOD IN YOU.

110
00:06:41,107 --> 00:06:43,076
THAT'S WHY
I DIDN'T TRY TO DODGE.

111
00:06:43,109 --> 00:06:45,546
YOU COULD HAVE
KILLED ME JUST NOW,

112
00:06:45,612 --> 00:06:47,848
BUT YOU STAYED YOUR HAND.

113
00:06:47,914 --> 00:06:49,115
Speedwagon: LOOK AT HIS FACE.

114
00:06:49,215 --> 00:06:51,284
IT'S LIKE ALL THE RAGE
AND HATRED HE HAD

115
00:06:51,351 --> 00:06:53,053
WHEN DIO BROUGHT HIM BACK
ARE GONE.

116
00:06:53,119 --> 00:06:54,454
HIS FEATURES ARE SO GENTLE,

117
00:06:54,555 --> 00:06:57,257
HE COULD BE A BLOKE CATCHING UP
WITH HIS OLDEST MATE.

118
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:59,726
Blueford: YOU STOOD THERE
LIKE A STATUE,

119
00:06:59,793 --> 00:07:02,135
READY TO TAKE THE FATAL BLOW.

120
00:07:02,202 --> 00:07:06,206
OBLIVION BECKONED,
BUT YOU PUT YOUR TRUST IN ME.

121
00:07:06,272 --> 00:07:09,142
YOUR FAITH IN HUMAN GOODNESS
IS RARE.

122
00:07:09,242 --> 00:07:10,877
( coughs )

123
00:07:10,944 --> 00:07:12,245
( chuckles )

124
00:07:12,312 --> 00:07:15,649
ONCE I'D HAVE RAILED
AGAINST THE PAIN I FEEL.

125
00:07:15,716 --> 00:07:17,918
NOW, GOING TO MY RIGHTFUL END,

126
00:07:17,984 --> 00:07:20,587
I CHERISH
ALL THAT PROVES ME HUMAN.

127
00:07:20,654 --> 00:07:22,656
IT GIVES ME JOY.

128
00:07:22,723 --> 00:07:24,958
THE EMBERS DULL WITHIN ME,

129
00:07:24,991 --> 00:07:26,627
BUT I AM TRANQUIL.

130
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:29,663
THERE IS NO BITTERNESS LEFT.

131
00:07:29,730 --> 00:07:32,498
WHAT IRONY TO LIVE YET AGAIN,

132
00:07:32,566 --> 00:07:34,400
DYING WITH THANKS ON MY LIPS

133
00:07:34,467 --> 00:07:37,337
FOR THE VERY MAN
WHO SLAUGHTERS ME ANEW.

134
00:07:37,403 --> 00:07:40,507
I SHALL RETURN
TO MY ONE TRUE MASTER.

135
00:07:43,343 --> 00:07:47,013
I WOULD KNOW THE NAME
OF THE WARRIOR WHO BESTED ME.

136
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:49,750
WOULD YOU KINDLY
DO ME THAT HONOR?

137
00:07:49,816 --> 00:07:52,519
JoJo: IT'S JONATHAN JOESTAR.

138
00:07:52,619 --> 00:07:55,856
Blueford: SIR JONATHAN,
I LEAVE YOU THIS SWORD,

139
00:07:55,922 --> 00:07:58,124
GIVEN TO ME
BY MY PRECIOUS QUEEN,

140
00:07:58,191 --> 00:08:00,366
AND THE WORD ENGRAVED UPON IT.

141
00:08:00,433 --> 00:08:02,168
LUCK.

142
00:08:02,202 --> 00:08:07,373
BUT FIRST. LET ME AFFIX
MY OWN BENEDICTION.

143
00:08:07,473 --> 00:08:08,709
PLUCK.

144
00:08:08,775 --> 00:08:10,877
JoJo: SIR BLUEFORD.

145
00:08:10,977 --> 00:08:12,178
Blueford: HEH.

146
00:08:18,218 --> 00:08:20,186
JoJo: GO YOU TO YOUR REST.

147
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:23,189
LET NO ONE DOUBT
YOU HAVE EARNED IT, BLUEFORD.

148
00:08:25,325 --> 00:08:30,196
WHY? WHY DID I HAVE TO STRIKE
HIM DOWN TO REDEEM HIS SOUL?

149
00:08:30,230 --> 00:08:33,667
HE DIED ONCE BEFORE
WITH HATE IN HIS HEART,

150
00:08:33,734 --> 00:08:35,702
BUT HIS SPIRIT WAS STILL PURE.

151
00:08:35,736 --> 00:08:40,240
HE RETURNED NOT OUT OF CHOICE,
BUT DRAGGED ABOVE BY DIO'S EVIL,

152
00:08:40,306 --> 00:08:42,509
HIS EVIL AND THE MASK'S POWER.

153
00:08:42,576 --> 00:08:45,912
I WILL SEND THEM BOTH TO HELL
BEFORE THE DAWN!

154
00:08:46,012 --> 00:08:48,682
Speedwagon: JOJO,
HE'S RIGHT BEHIND YOU!

155
00:08:48,749 --> 00:08:49,983
( JoJo gasps )
TARUKUS!

156
00:08:50,050 --> 00:08:51,217
( Tarukus scoffs )

157
00:08:53,086 --> 00:08:54,688
‐ ( hisses )
‐ JoJo: YOU VILLAIN!

158
00:08:54,755 --> 00:08:58,158
THAT WAS THE ARMOR OF
A STEADFAST FRIEND AND COMRADE.

159
00:08:58,224 --> 00:09:00,160
HE DIED WITH HONOR AND DIGNITY.

160
00:09:00,226 --> 00:09:02,603
Tarukus: HE DIED
LIKE A SPINELESS DOG!

161
00:09:02,703 --> 00:09:04,871
HE WAS TOO CLEVER BY HALF,

162
00:09:04,938 --> 00:09:06,873
LIKED WINNING HIS FIGHTS
WITH THINKING.

163
00:09:06,940 --> 00:09:10,611
I JUST HIT 'EM
UNTIL THEY FALL TO PIECES!

164
00:09:10,677 --> 00:09:12,779
WHAT USE HAVE I GOT FOR CLEVER?

165
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:15,448
I CARRY A SWORD
AS TALL AS A MAN.

166
00:09:15,549 --> 00:09:18,451
NONE OF YOU
WILL GET AN EASY DEATH.

167
00:09:18,552 --> 00:09:22,723
( roars )

168
00:09:22,789 --> 00:09:25,191
♪

169
00:09:27,628 --> 00:09:29,530
( Poco gasping )

170
00:09:29,596 --> 00:09:30,864
( screams )

171
00:09:30,931 --> 00:09:32,599
♪

172
00:09:32,633 --> 00:09:35,235
Zeppeli: JOJO, NICE CATCH.

173
00:09:36,402 --> 00:09:38,705
Speedwagon:
THE CLIFF IS CRUMBLING!

174
00:09:39,973 --> 00:09:40,974
Zeppeli: HMM.

175
00:09:41,041 --> 00:09:42,743
THESE DEAD LEAVES.

176
00:09:42,809 --> 00:09:43,977
JOJO!

177
00:09:44,044 --> 00:09:44,978
JoJo: YES, SIR.

178
00:09:45,045 --> 00:09:48,915
( both inhale )

179
00:09:48,982 --> 00:09:52,986
LIFE MAGNETISM OVERDRIVE!

180
00:09:54,487 --> 00:09:55,455
( Tarukus growls )

181
00:09:56,723 --> 00:10:00,934
( roars )

182
00:10:01,001 --> 00:10:04,538
JoJo: HURRY, POCO, SPEEDWAGON!
GRAB ON!

183
00:10:11,277 --> 00:10:14,447
Narrator: ALL HUMAN BEINGS,
WHETHER ADEPT AT HAMON OR NOT,

184
00:10:14,548 --> 00:10:17,350
CONSTANTLY EXUDE
A WEAK MAGNETIC FIELD.

185
00:10:17,417 --> 00:10:20,787
AN OVERDRIVE CAN INCREASE
THE POWER OF THAT FIELD.

186
00:10:20,887 --> 00:10:23,289
JOJO AND ZEPPELI
SENT IT INTO THE LEAVES,

187
00:10:23,356 --> 00:10:25,859
DRAWING THEM TOGETHER
INTO A SOLID SHEET.

188
00:10:25,926 --> 00:10:27,894
Poco: W‐WOW.

189
00:10:27,961 --> 00:10:28,962
BYE.

190
00:10:29,029 --> 00:10:30,797
( laughs )

191
00:10:30,897 --> 00:10:32,365
( Tarukus growls )

192
00:10:32,432 --> 00:10:35,201
Poco: WE'RE FLYING.
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

193
00:10:35,268 --> 00:10:36,603
I BET YOU'RE MAGICIANS, HUH?

194
00:10:36,637 --> 00:10:39,305
YOU'D HAVE TO BE, RIGHT?
HOW DID YOU LEARN TO DO

195
00:10:39,405 --> 00:10:41,642
ALL OF THESE NEAT SPELLS
IN THE FIRST PLACE?

196
00:10:41,742 --> 00:10:43,276
Speedwagon: DAMN GOOD QUESTION.

197
00:10:43,309 --> 00:10:46,980
I'VE BEEN WATCHING 'EM DO IT,
AND I STILL PINCH MYSELF.

198
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,782
OI, BARON, WHAT'S THE STORY?

199
00:10:48,815 --> 00:10:50,150
WE'RE NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

200
00:10:50,216 --> 00:10:53,987
HOW ON EARTH DID YOU PICK UP
ALL THIS MUMBO JUMBO?

201
00:10:57,924 --> 00:10:59,626
( seabirds calling )

202
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:02,135
♪

203
00:11:02,168 --> 00:11:05,438
Zeppeli: MANY YEARS AGO,
MY TRAVELS TOOK ME TO INDIA,

204
00:11:05,506 --> 00:11:07,340
WHERE I DISCOVERED
A MYSTERIOUS MAN.

205
00:11:07,407 --> 00:11:10,844
HE CALLED HIMSELF A DOCTOR,
THOUGH HE WAS VERY YOUNG

206
00:11:10,911 --> 00:11:13,179
AND LACKED
ALL THE TOOLS OF THE TRADE.

207
00:11:13,246 --> 00:11:14,748
LITTLE DID I KNOW

208
00:11:14,815 --> 00:11:17,851
HE WAS MORE POTENT OF A MEDIC
THAN I'D EVER ENCOUNTERED.

209
00:11:17,918 --> 00:11:20,153
HE TOOK A GANGRENOUS LIMB
IN HIS HANDS

210
00:11:20,186 --> 00:11:22,288
AND HEALED IT
WITH LIGHT FROM WITHIN.

211
00:11:22,355 --> 00:11:26,026
THAT WAS THE DAY
I LEARNED OF HAMON.

212
00:11:26,092 --> 00:11:27,360
I'D BEEN LOOKING FOR SOMETHING

213
00:11:27,427 --> 00:11:29,195
WITH WHICH TO FIGHT
THE STONE MASK'S EVIL,

214
00:11:29,295 --> 00:11:31,497
AND IN HAMON, I HAD FOUND IT.

215
00:11:31,532 --> 00:11:34,267
EAGER TO LEARN,
I CROSSED INTO TIBET

216
00:11:34,334 --> 00:11:35,702
AND UP THE SALWEEN RIVER

217
00:11:35,802 --> 00:11:39,372
IN SEARCH OF HE
WHO HAD TAUGHT THE YOUNG HEALER.

218
00:11:45,846 --> 00:11:49,149
HIS NAME WAS TONPETTY.

219
00:11:56,222 --> 00:11:57,524
( Zeppeli gasps )

220
00:12:00,827 --> 00:12:06,172
Tonpetty: STRANGER, THESE EYES
OF MINE HAVE SEEN YOUR FUTURE.

221
00:12:06,239 --> 00:12:10,711
IF YOU PURSUE THE MYSTERIES
OF HAMON AS MY PUPIL,

222
00:12:10,744 --> 00:12:12,579
YOUR FATE IS SEALED.

223
00:12:12,646 --> 00:12:16,216
THE DAY WILL COME WHEN THIS
WILL BE THE DEATH OF YOU.

224
00:12:16,249 --> 00:12:18,985
Zeppeli: I UNDERSTAND.

225
00:12:19,052 --> 00:12:23,657
IF I MUST DIE TO END THIS QUEST,
SO BE IT.

226
00:12:23,724 --> 00:12:25,659
♪

227
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:28,729
( Hamon crackling )

228
00:12:30,931 --> 00:12:34,668
MASTER TONPETTY'S PROPHECY
IS NEVER FAR FROM MY MIND,

229
00:12:34,735 --> 00:12:37,671
BUT I CANNOT TELL THEM,
NOT EVEN JOJO.

230
00:12:37,738 --> 00:12:39,072
Speedwagon: BARON...

231
00:12:39,105 --> 00:12:41,041
( whooshing )

232
00:12:41,107 --> 00:12:42,543
SO THAT SOUND,

233
00:12:42,609 --> 00:12:45,278
THAT'S PART OF HAMON
DOING ITS THING, YEAH?

234
00:12:45,378 --> 00:12:47,113
( JoJo gasps ) HARDLY.

235
00:12:47,213 --> 00:12:48,949
Poco: LOOK OUT! IT'S TARUKUS!

236
00:12:49,049 --> 00:12:52,118
( Tarukus roars )

237
00:12:57,223 --> 00:13:00,767
( Tarukus roars )

238
00:13:00,801 --> 00:13:02,302
Zeppeli: HE'S INSANE,

239
00:13:02,368 --> 00:13:06,239
LEAPING FROM THAT HEIGHT
JUST TO GIVE CHASE TO HIS FOES.

240
00:13:08,542 --> 00:13:10,310
THERE'S A GOODLY AMOUNT OF HAMON

241
00:13:10,376 --> 00:13:12,312
HOLDING THESE LEAVES TOGETHER,
YOU BRUTE,

242
00:13:12,378 --> 00:13:14,715
PAINFUL TO THE TOUCH
FOR THE UNDEAD.

243
00:13:14,781 --> 00:13:16,983
‐ JoJo: WHAT'S THAT?
‐ Poco: THAT'S WHERE THE KNIGHTS

244
00:13:17,083 --> 00:13:18,919
USED TO TRAIN IN THE OLDEN DAYS.

245
00:13:18,985 --> 00:13:20,153
JoJo: LEAP TO SAFETY, EVERYONE,

246
00:13:20,253 --> 00:13:22,656
BEFORE WE GET
SWATTED OUT OF THE SKY!

247
00:13:22,756 --> 00:13:24,758
( Poco yells )

248
00:13:28,962 --> 00:13:30,664
Speedwagon: CRAZY BLIGHTER.

249
00:13:30,731 --> 00:13:33,299
HE JUST SLAMMED HIMSELF
STRAIGHT INTO THE TOWER.

250
00:13:33,333 --> 00:13:35,235
Zeppeli: YES,
AND THANK YOUR LUCKY STARS

251
00:13:35,301 --> 00:13:36,770
THAT HE DID, SPEEDWAGON.

252
00:13:36,837 --> 00:13:39,573
UNLIKE THEIR MASTER,
DIO'S MINIONS CAN'T REGENERATE,

253
00:13:39,640 --> 00:13:42,308
SO THAT SHOULD BE THE LAST
WE SEE OF THAT BEAST.

254
00:13:42,342 --> 00:13:43,744
( JoJo gasps )

255
00:13:43,810 --> 00:13:45,746
♪

256
00:13:46,947 --> 00:13:49,182
( Tarukus growls )

257
00:13:49,249 --> 00:13:51,184
Zeppeli: HOW DID‐‐
HE SHOULD BE MINCEMEAT.

258
00:13:51,284 --> 00:13:53,687
EVEN IN DEATH,
HE HAS A WILL OF IRON.

259
00:13:53,754 --> 00:13:56,923
HOW DOES HIS BODY ENDURE
UNDER SUCH PUNISHMENT?

260
00:13:56,990 --> 00:13:58,859
Speedwagon: HE'S CLIMBING UP.

261
00:13:58,959 --> 00:14:00,260
Zeppeli: WE CAN'T DESTROY DIO

262
00:14:00,326 --> 00:14:02,302
WHILE THIS MONSTER
DOGS OUR STEPS.

263
00:14:02,368 --> 00:14:04,538
IT SEEMS WE HAVE
NO OTHER CHOICE.

264
00:14:04,638 --> 00:14:07,307
TARUKUS MEETS HIS DOOM
HERE AND NOW.

265
00:14:07,373 --> 00:14:09,510
JOJO, THIS WILL BE PERILOUS.

266
00:14:09,543 --> 00:14:11,945
GET THE LAD TO SAFETY WITHIN.

267
00:14:12,012 --> 00:14:14,615
( Tarukus growling )

268
00:14:14,681 --> 00:14:15,649
( chuckles )

269
00:14:22,022 --> 00:14:23,056
( clank )

270
00:14:23,123 --> 00:14:24,324
( JoJo gasps )

271
00:14:25,225 --> 00:14:26,560
THIS DOOR...

272
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:29,029
‐ SOMETHING'S ODD ABOUT IT.
‐ Poco: BE CAREFUL.

273
00:14:29,062 --> 00:14:32,132
THIS IS WHERE THEY USED TO TRAIN
THE KNIGHTS HOW TO KILL PEOPLE.

274
00:14:32,198 --> 00:14:35,001
THEY SAY
IT'S FULL OF BOOBY TRAPS.

275
00:14:35,068 --> 00:14:36,002
( chain jangles )

276
00:14:36,069 --> 00:14:37,003
Speedwagon: DUCK, JOJO!

277
00:14:37,070 --> 00:14:38,839
SOMETHING'S COMING AT YA!

278
00:14:38,905 --> 00:14:40,406
( JoJo gasps )

279
00:14:41,374 --> 00:14:43,744
‐ Poco: OH, NO!
‐ Zeppeli: JOJO!

280
00:14:47,247 --> 00:14:48,682
JoJo: WHO ENSNARED ME?

281
00:14:51,351 --> 00:14:52,485
TARUKUS.

282
00:14:52,553 --> 00:14:55,255
Tarukus: YES. CAUGHT YOU GOOD.

283
00:14:55,355 --> 00:14:56,890
YOU'RE FLEET OF FOOT,
LITTLE MAN,

284
00:14:56,923 --> 00:14:59,860
BUT NOW YOU AND ME
ARE CHAINED TO EACH OTHER.

285
00:14:59,926 --> 00:15:03,103
YOU GOT NOWHERE TO RUN.

286
00:15:03,169 --> 00:15:04,437
( JoJo gasps )

287
00:15:04,538 --> 00:15:05,739
Narrator: JOJO HAD WANDERED

288
00:15:05,772 --> 00:15:08,008
INTO THE LAIR
OF THE TWO‐HEADED DRAGON,

289
00:15:08,074 --> 00:15:11,444
AN ANCIENT SPARRING GROUND AND
HOME OF THE CHAIN DEATH‐MATCH.

290
00:15:11,545 --> 00:15:13,914
Tarukus: I KILLED 48 MEN HERE.

291
00:15:13,947 --> 00:15:17,450
TAKING A LIFE'S AN ART FORM,
AND I'M A MASTER.

292
00:15:17,551 --> 00:15:20,120
( Zeppeli grunting )

293
00:15:20,220 --> 00:15:23,189
Speedwagon: THAT'S ENOUGH.
YOU CAN'T PUNCH THROUGH IT.

294
00:15:23,256 --> 00:15:25,291
THAT DOOR IS SOLID IRON.

295
00:15:25,358 --> 00:15:28,629
Poco: GOODNESS. HE'S BATTERED
HIS KNUCKLES BLOODY AGAINST IT.

296
00:15:28,729 --> 00:15:30,931
Zeppeli: HAMON IS
VERY VERSATILE,

297
00:15:30,964 --> 00:15:33,033
BUT IT'S MEANT TO BE
USED AS A RAPIER,

298
00:15:33,099 --> 00:15:34,267
NOT AS A SLEDGEHAMMER.

299
00:15:34,300 --> 00:15:36,302
BRICKS I COULD BEAT TO A POWDER,

300
00:15:36,369 --> 00:15:38,138
BUT THIS DOOR IS TOO STRONG.

301
00:15:38,238 --> 00:15:40,240
JOJO FACES A DARKER DILEMMA.

302
00:15:40,306 --> 00:15:41,575
THAT CHAIN ABOUT HIS NECK

303
00:15:41,642 --> 00:15:43,544
IS MORE THAN RIPPLE ENERGY
CAN OVERCOME.

304
00:15:43,610 --> 00:15:46,279
Tarukus: BREAKING OUT
OF THAT COLLAR IS IMPOSSIBLE,

305
00:15:46,312 --> 00:15:48,715
AND YOU'LL NEED
THE KEY TO UNLOCK IT.

306
00:15:48,782 --> 00:15:50,551
TOO BAD IT'S RIGHT HERE.

307
00:15:51,885 --> 00:15:52,986
DURING A DEATH MATCH,

308
00:15:53,086 --> 00:15:56,389
THE DOOR TO THE OUTSIDE
IS FASHIONED TO LOCK TIGHT.

309
00:15:56,456 --> 00:15:58,424
JUST AS I HAVE THE KEY
TO YOUR COLLAR,

310
00:15:58,491 --> 00:16:00,426
YOU HAVE THE ONE
THAT GOES TO MINE.

311
00:16:00,493 --> 00:16:03,069
THEREFORE, THE ONLY WAY
THAT EITHER OF US

312
00:16:03,136 --> 00:16:05,271
IS GOING TO GET OUT OF HERE...

313
00:16:05,338 --> 00:16:06,339
( JoJo gags )

314
00:16:06,406 --> 00:16:08,742
IS BY TAKING THE OTHER'S HEAD!

315
00:16:08,809 --> 00:16:11,144
( JoJo yells )

316
00:16:11,177 --> 00:16:14,815
OVERDRIVE!

317
00:16:14,848 --> 00:16:16,817
( gasping )

318
00:16:21,021 --> 00:16:23,957
THE CHAIN IS TOUCHING
THE STONE CEILING,

319
00:16:24,024 --> 00:16:27,293
SO THE HAMON LACKS
A DIRECT PATH INTO TARUKUS.

320
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:29,530
( Tarukus growls )

321
00:16:31,131 --> 00:16:33,667
( bone cracks )

322
00:16:33,700 --> 00:16:36,603
JoJo: HE'S BROKEN
THE BONE IN MY FOREARM.

323
00:16:36,670 --> 00:16:38,639
( gasps )
IT'S A SIMPLE THING TO FIX.

324
00:16:38,705 --> 00:16:40,974
A LITTLE HAMON,
AND I'M GOOD AS NEW.

325
00:16:41,041 --> 00:16:42,876
BUT IN ORDER TO USE HAMON,

326
00:16:42,976 --> 00:16:45,879
I NEED TO BE FREE
OF THIS DAMNABLE COLLAR.

327
00:16:45,979 --> 00:16:47,814
I CAN'T BREATHE.

328
00:16:47,881 --> 00:16:49,950
( door rattles )

329
00:16:51,051 --> 00:16:52,018
Zeppeli: JOJO!

330
00:16:52,052 --> 00:16:53,820
Poco: OH, NO.

331
00:16:53,887 --> 00:16:57,057
THIS IS ALL SO FRIGHTENING,
I THINK I WET MYSELF.

332
00:16:57,123 --> 00:17:00,794
THIS VILLAGE WAS SAFE
UNTIL THESE MEN ARRIVED.

333
00:17:00,861 --> 00:17:03,003
I'M IN DANGER HERE.
YOU NEED TO GET AWAY

334
00:17:03,069 --> 00:17:05,238
FROM ALL THIS FIGHTING
ON THE DOUBLE, POCO.

335
00:17:05,338 --> 00:17:07,407
Speedwagon: I SEE A LEVER,
BARON ZEPPELI.

336
00:17:07,473 --> 00:17:08,709
NO TELLING FOR CERTAIN,

337
00:17:08,742 --> 00:17:11,411
BUT I THINK PULLING ON IT
WILL OPEN THIS DOOR.

338
00:17:11,512 --> 00:17:12,579
Zeppeli: FIGHTING TARUKUS

339
00:17:12,646 --> 00:17:14,180
IS A DAUNTING ENOUGH TASK
AS IT IS,

340
00:17:14,247 --> 00:17:17,050
NEVER MIND DOING IT FRESH
OUT OF A BATTLE WITH BLUEFORD.

341
00:17:17,083 --> 00:17:18,051
( blood spurts )

342
00:17:18,084 --> 00:17:19,185
COME HELL OR HIGH WATER,

343
00:17:19,252 --> 00:17:22,155
WE MUST FIND A WAY
TO GET IN THERE AND HELP HIM.

344
00:17:22,222 --> 00:17:25,091
Speedwagon: UHH! IT'S LOCKED UP
TIGHTER THAN A NUNNERY.

345
00:17:27,427 --> 00:17:28,995
♪

346
00:17:30,597 --> 00:17:32,566
Poco: IT'S SO NARROW.

347
00:17:32,599 --> 00:17:36,336
TRY AS THEY MIGHT, THEY COULD
NEVER SQUEEZE THROUGH,

348
00:17:36,402 --> 00:17:37,538
BUT...

349
00:17:39,205 --> 00:17:41,908
MAYBE I COULD.

350
00:17:41,942 --> 00:17:43,710
( Tarukus yells )

351
00:17:44,578 --> 00:17:46,079
Zeppeli: BLAST IT!

352
00:17:46,112 --> 00:17:49,249
WE COULD BATTER THIS DOOR
'TIL JUDGMENT DAY TO NO AVAIL.

353
00:17:49,282 --> 00:17:50,383
WE'LL HAVE TO USE

354
00:17:50,450 --> 00:17:51,952
THE CLIFFSIDE ENTRANCE
TARUKUS USED.

355
00:17:52,052 --> 00:17:53,720
Speedwagon: BUT THAT'LL
TAKE TOO MUCH TIME,

356
00:17:53,787 --> 00:17:55,121
TIME THAT HE DON'T GOT.

357
00:17:55,188 --> 00:17:57,558
Zeppeli: I KNOW,
BUT WE'VE NO OTHER CHOICE.

358
00:17:57,624 --> 00:18:00,026
( Speedwagon growls )

359
00:18:00,093 --> 00:18:03,036
ALWAYS
ON THE BLEEDIN' SIDELINES.

360
00:18:03,103 --> 00:18:04,638
I'M POWERLESS.

361
00:18:04,705 --> 00:18:06,873
THERE'S NOTHING
I CAN DO TO HELP.

362
00:18:06,940 --> 00:18:09,075
Boy: LOOK AT ME, BRAT.
I'M TALKING TO YOU.

363
00:18:09,142 --> 00:18:10,977
‐ ( Poco sobs )
‐ Boy: I SAID LOOK AT ME.

364
00:18:11,077 --> 00:18:12,879
‐ ( boy #2 laughs )
‐ Boy: ARE YOU STUPID OR WHAT?

365
00:18:12,946 --> 00:18:14,815
Boy #3: HE'S SUCH
A LITTLE SCAREDY‐CAT.

366
00:18:14,915 --> 00:18:17,618
Boy #4: WHAT A BABY.
HE'S SHAKING LIKE A LEAF.

367
00:18:17,651 --> 00:18:19,285
Boy #2: LOOK, FELLAS.
LOOK AT HIM.

368
00:18:19,319 --> 00:18:21,087
Boy #1: AW,
IS THE BABY GONNA CRY?

369
00:18:23,657 --> 00:18:25,826
( boys laughing )

370
00:18:29,663 --> 00:18:31,264
Boy #2: HEY. LOOK.

371
00:18:31,331 --> 00:18:32,666
Boy #1: HMM?

372
00:18:34,100 --> 00:18:36,603
( boy #4 gasps ) COME ON!
LET'S GET OUTTA HERE.

373
00:18:40,173 --> 00:18:42,108
Poco: SIS, IT'S YOU.

374
00:18:42,175 --> 00:18:43,510
Sister: POCO, REALLY?

375
00:18:43,610 --> 00:18:45,812
YOU'RE LETTING THOSE BOYS
BULLY YOU AGAIN?

376
00:18:45,846 --> 00:18:48,014
THEY DO THIS ALL THE TIME.

377
00:18:48,114 --> 00:18:50,851
WHY NOT TRY
STANDING UP TO THEM FOR ONCE?

378
00:18:50,917 --> 00:18:54,354
Poco: I'LL BLOODY THEIR NOSES!
I WILL!

379
00:18:54,420 --> 00:18:56,790
Sister: WHEN? TOMORROW?
IN A YEAR?

380
00:18:56,857 --> 00:18:58,792
Poco: UH, I DON'T KNOW.

381
00:19:01,034 --> 00:19:02,168
Sister: POCO...

382
00:19:02,202 --> 00:19:05,205
WHAT FRIGHTENS YOU
MORE THAN ANYTHING ELSE?

383
00:19:07,608 --> 00:19:09,209
( Poco yelps )

384
00:19:09,275 --> 00:19:12,378
Sister: I KNOW THAT HURT,
BUT YOU'RE STILL IN ONE PIECE.

385
00:19:12,445 --> 00:19:15,015
PAIN'S NOT THE WORST THING.

386
00:19:15,882 --> 00:19:17,317
THERE'S SOMETHING FAR WORSE.

387
00:19:17,383 --> 00:19:18,852
Poco: HUH?

388
00:19:18,885 --> 00:19:21,888
Sister: IT'S GROWING UP
BEING TOO AFRAID TO DO ANYTHING.

389
00:19:21,988 --> 00:19:24,691
WHAT KIND OF A LIFE
WOULD THAT BE?

390
00:19:25,726 --> 00:19:29,062
Poco: I'M SORRY, SIS.

391
00:19:29,129 --> 00:19:30,731
( sister sighs )

392
00:19:30,797 --> 00:19:31,798
( Poco crying )

393
00:19:31,865 --> 00:19:34,300
Sister: IT'S ALL RIGHT, POCO.

394
00:19:34,367 --> 00:19:37,037
LET'S GET YOU HOME
AND INTO SOME CLEAN CLOTHES.

395
00:19:38,505 --> 00:19:40,641
♪

396
00:19:46,580 --> 00:19:48,582
( thump )

397
00:19:48,682 --> 00:19:50,483
Zeppeli: POCO!

398
00:19:50,551 --> 00:19:52,218
Speedwagon: A WINDOW.

399
00:19:52,252 --> 00:19:53,687
OI, LAD! THAT'S BRAVE,

400
00:19:53,754 --> 00:19:56,089
BUT GOIN' IN THERE
IS GONNA BE THE END OF YA!

401
00:19:56,156 --> 00:19:58,091
Zeppeli: SPEEDWAGON,
GET THE BOY DOWN!

402
00:19:58,158 --> 00:20:00,934
A BUTCHER LIKE TARUKUS
DOESN'T CARE WHO HE KILLS!

403
00:20:01,001 --> 00:20:03,169
HE'LL CRUSH POCO UNDERFOOT
LIKE A BUG!

404
00:20:03,203 --> 00:20:07,040
Speedwagon: COME ON, NOW!
ENOUGH OF THIS NONSENSE, POCO!

405
00:20:10,176 --> 00:20:13,313
Poco: JUST THINK OF WHAT'S
GONNA HAPPEN TO WIND KNIGHTS LOT

406
00:20:13,379 --> 00:20:14,881
IF THESE MONSTERS WIN.

407
00:20:14,981 --> 00:20:19,052
IF THAT JOJO GUY GETS KILLED
IN HERE, THEY'LL ATTACK US NEXT.

408
00:20:19,152 --> 00:20:21,522
WHAT IF THEY HURT SIS?

409
00:20:21,555 --> 00:20:23,524
( bell jingles )

410
00:20:23,557 --> 00:20:27,193
I HAVE TO KEEP HER SAFE,
NO MATTER WHAT.

411
00:20:28,394 --> 00:20:30,396
HEY, SIS!

412
00:20:30,463 --> 00:20:33,033
I'M STANDING UP TO THEM NOW!

413
00:20:33,066 --> 00:20:35,536
JoJo: STAY BACK! HE'LL KILL YOU.

414
00:20:35,569 --> 00:20:36,737
( Tarukus growls )

415
00:20:36,803 --> 00:20:39,339
DO NOT INTERFERE, YOU BRAT!

416
00:20:39,405 --> 00:20:40,907
( JoJo roars )

417
00:20:44,678 --> 00:20:45,579
( both scream )

418
00:20:45,679 --> 00:20:48,414
JoJo: POCO!

419
00:20:48,481 --> 00:20:50,083
Poco: IT HURT A LOT,

420
00:20:50,150 --> 00:20:54,420
BUT I'M STILL IN ONE PIECE,
SO IT'S FINE.

421
00:20:54,487 --> 00:20:56,590
♪

422
00:21:01,835 --> 00:21:02,936
( lock clicks )

423
00:21:04,705 --> 00:21:08,074
I WAS BRAVE, HUH?

424
00:21:08,108 --> 00:21:10,944
( laughs )

425
00:21:11,044 --> 00:21:13,780
Speedwagon:
BRAVE AS A BEAR, MY LAD.

426
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:16,717
TAKE HEART.
IT'S NOTHING THAT WON'T HEAL.

427
00:21:17,751 --> 00:21:19,119
GET HIM, BARON! GO!

428
00:21:19,185 --> 00:21:23,289
GIVE THAT HULKING BASTARD
THE WHAT‐FOR.

429
00:21:23,389 --> 00:21:26,359
♪

430
00:21:32,465 --> 00:21:34,434
ZEPPELI?

431
00:21:34,467 --> 00:21:35,969
Tonpetty: THE DAY WILL COME

432
00:21:36,069 --> 00:21:39,540
WHEN THIS WILL BE
THE DEATH OF YOU.

433
00:21:39,606 --> 00:21:40,974
Zeppeli: INFINE.

434
00:21:41,074 --> 00:21:44,811
IS TONIGHT THE NIGHT
THAT I GO TO MY GRAVE?

435
00:21:44,911 --> 00:21:46,046
( Speedwagon gasps )

436
00:21:46,112 --> 00:21:48,582
Zeppeli: FATE IS
A FICKLE MISTRESS,

437
00:21:48,649 --> 00:21:51,251
BUT I CANNOT DENY HER.

438
00:21:51,317 --> 00:21:52,418
Speedwagon: ZEPPELI...

439
00:21:52,485 --> 00:21:55,989
WHY DO YOU SOUND SO DIRE?

440
00:21:57,891 --> 00:21:59,425
( Tarukus growls )

441
00:21:59,492 --> 00:22:01,434
♪

442
00:22:14,180 --> 00:22:17,651
♪ I'LL BE THE ROUNDABOUT

443
00:22:17,684 --> 00:22:21,487
♪ THE WORDS
WILL MAKE YOU OUT AND OUT ♪

444
00:22:21,522 --> 00:22:26,793
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

445
00:22:26,860 --> 00:22:29,095
♪ CALL IT MORNING
DRIVING THROUGH THE SOUND ♪

446
00:22:29,162 --> 00:22:34,200
♪ AND IN AND OUT THE VALLEY

447
00:22:41,441 --> 00:22:44,778
♪ THE MUSIC DANCE AND SING

448
00:22:44,845 --> 00:22:48,481
♪ THEY MAKE THE CHILDREN
REALLY RING ♪

449
00:22:48,549 --> 00:22:53,720
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

450
00:22:53,820 --> 00:22:56,389
♪ CALL IT MORNING
DRIVING THROUGH THE SOUND ♪

451
00:22:56,489 --> 00:23:00,393
♪ AND IN AND OUT THE VALLEY

452
00:23:00,460 --> 00:23:03,970
♪ IN AND AROUND THE LAKE

453
00:23:04,037 --> 00:23:06,372
♪ MOUNTAINS COME
OUT OF THE SKY ♪

454
00:23:06,406 --> 00:23:08,474
♪ AND THEY STAND THERE

455
00:23:10,877 --> 00:23:13,313
♪ ONE MILE OVER,
WE'LL BE THERE ♪

456
00:23:13,379 --> 00:23:15,181
♪ AND WE'LL SEE YOU

457
00:23:17,584 --> 00:23:21,755
♪ 10 TRUE SUMMERS, WE'LL BE
THERE AND LAUGHING, TOO ♪

458
00:23:23,990 --> 00:23:26,927
♪ 24 BEFORE, MY LOVE,
YOU'LL SEE ♪

459
00:23:26,993 --> 00:23:31,197
♪ I'LL BE THERE WITH YOU

460
00:23:38,739 --> 00:23:40,440
♪

461
00:23:40,541 --> 00:23:43,844
Speedwagon: THIS BLOODY SAVAGERY
IS UNBELIEVABLE!

462
00:23:43,910 --> 00:23:46,279
JoJo: OH, NO! TARAKUS!

463
00:23:46,379 --> 00:23:48,348
Tarakus: PATHETIC
WASTE OF FLESH!

464
00:23:48,414 --> 00:23:49,750
Zeppeli: JOJO, TAKE IT!

465
00:23:49,783 --> 00:23:51,852
MAKE IT YOURS!

